  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"UUUUFtxN\">谢 <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-pan-57-90\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"1043\">小潘</a> 邀请.</p><p data-pid=\"Fsb7G2-Q\">嗯.题主说的情况确实如此.我觉得原因可能如下.</p><p data-pid=\"LdF2extI\">1.<b>环境因素.比如空气污染,水源污染,<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=143730717&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">食物污染<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b>等等.</p><p data-pid=\"4dqXmH9u\">2.<b>生活规律,和饮食习俗被打破</b>,人类这个物种还没来得及适应.比如现在很多慢性病某种情况算是营养过剩,比如肥胖,<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=143730717&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=2%E5%9E%8B%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">2型糖尿病<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>,高血脂等等.</p><p data-pid=\"w87WXBhT\">3.<b>生活和工作压力变大,造成心理压力变大</b>,记得有人说过,现在80%以上的人都有心理问题.所以我现在很怂的.只要没到底线,基本都是骂不还口的..........除了心理健康问题,还有不少疾病是<b>心理应激影响<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=143730717&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">免疫系统<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b>引起的.比如常见的,口疮,胃溃疡等等,...........</p><p data-pid=\"1lQI1LHr\">4,<b>不孕不育跟工业化有很大问题</b>.比如常见的<b>环境雌激素</b>[1-7].</p><p data-pid=\"9dfhVLKo\">总结,<b>现代生活环境和生活方式跟以前变化很大,特别是近一二百年的变化,而人类的自然演化还没来得及适应,所以出现很多情况是正常反应.</b></p><p data-pid=\"qaZl9M67\">所以.<b>如果无法改变环境,就努力适应它吧</b>......鲁迅</p><p data-pid=\"Hzk_VSvl\">参考</p><p data-pid=\"I_-pjKfT\">1,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFD2014%26filename%3DZYJK201420053%26v%3DMTk0NDhIOVhPcjQ5QVo0UjhlWDFMdXhZUzdEaDFUM3FUcldNMUZyQ1VSTE9mWk9kb0Z5SGhXN3pLUHpUQlpiRzQ%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">环境雌激素与不孕不育的相关性 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"fTZxnxet\">2.<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFD2006%26filename%3DSFCZ200612007%26v%3DMTQ0OTZyV00xRnJDVVJMT2ZaT2RvRnlIaFc3ek1OaXZJZExHNEh0Zk5yWTlGWTRSOGVYMUx1eFlTN0RoMVQzcVQ%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">环境雌激素与不孕不育 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"76Bs9SHj\">3,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFDHIS2%26filename%3DSYYY201310050%26v%3DMzE0MTBoMVQzcVRyV00xRnJDVVJMT2ZaT2RvRnlEa1Vydk9OalRTZDdHNEg5TE5yNDlBWklSOGVYMUx1eFlTN0Q%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">环境雌激素双酚A对男性生殖细胞影响的研究进展 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"EhdMRep3\">4,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFD2004%26filename%3DHJHX200406020%26v%3DMDM3NzJGeURrVTcvQUxTZkRkckc0SHRYTXFZOUhaSVI4ZVgxTHV4WVM3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkxPZlpPZG8%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">环境雌激素对男性生育因子的破坏作用 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"DoJ4FdOJ\">5,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFDLAST2018%26filename%3DCQSF201801003%26v%3DMDExMDg3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkxPZlpPZG9GeURrVTd2SkpqellhTEc0SDluTXJvOUZaNFI4ZVgxTHV4WVM%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">环境剂量的多种环境雌激素长期暴露阻断斑马鱼成鱼精子发生 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"J5ME_Z-5\">6,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFDLAST2017%26filename%3DLCWX201751127%26v%3DMTc4MzVIWTRSOGVYMUx1eFlTN0RoMVQzcVRyV00xRnJDVVJMT2ZaT2RvRnlEa1VMM0pLUzdjZHJHNEg5YkpybzU%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">扬州市地面水雌激素类化合物污染水平调查研究 - 中国知网</a>,这篇研究说,扬州环境<b>基本合格</b>.</p><p data-pid=\"OUn1ggqQ\">7,<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFDLAST2015%26filename%3DNKXB201511016%26v%3DMzIyNTExVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkxPZlpPZG9GeURrVUx2TUt5YlRiTEc0SDlUTnJvOUVZb1I4ZVgxTHV4WVM3RGg%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">双酚A对男性生殖毒性的研究进展 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"5SgW8b9_\">等等吧.这类研究很多,就不贴了.<b>不过大家该吃吃,该喝喝,反正大家也改变不了什么</b>.</p><p data-pid=\"WD0pBB2g\">.......UP脑洞.....................</p><p data-pid=\"JcSdTkVR\">既然你看到这里了.就<b>附送个脑洞</b>..我刚才查文献的时候.开了个脑洞.所以去查了下.居然还真有这研究.</p><p data-pid=\"DiuQK8uu\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//kns.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx%3Fdbcode%3DCJFQ%26dbname%3DCJFD2013%26filename%3DDWXY201305009%26v%3DMDA2OTkxRnJDVVJMT2ZaT2RvRnlEbFY3ck9JVHJUZDdHNEg5TE1xbzlGYllSOGVYMUx1eFlTN0RoMVQzcVRyV00%3D\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">围产期克罗米酚处理改变雄性小鼠性取向 - 中国知网</a></p><p data-pid=\"jlVqrHpZ\">由于体内激素水平的变化<b>,围产期和青春期是决定动物大脑发育的关键和敏感时期,而大脑发育是成年动物性取向行为的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=143730717&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">生物基础<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b>。该研究根据这一假说,<b>对实验动物分别于围产期给予药物处理或于青春期予以阉割,并观察其个体成年后的性取向行为</b>。结果显示,围产期克罗米酚(clomiphene citrate)处理9 d(分娩前3天到生育后6天)和14 d(分娩前7天到生育后7天)组,<b>雄性后代的同性取向和雌性化行为明显增多</b>,而正常生长状态下的21日龄雄性后代经阉割后,其性取向无明显改变。即<b>围产期抑制雌激素,可导致雄性小鼠大脑<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=143730717&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E9%9B%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">雌性化<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>,产生同性取向,且围产期雌激素对动物雄性化的影响较青春期更为明显.</b></p><h2>[UC新闻]<b>震惊..现在女装大佬变多的原因竟然是</b>.........</h2><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-aa0589780dd536aa458c24be689b4b08_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"343\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-aa0589780dd536aa458c24be689b4b08\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa84c340ebd7f2d2643637c12021b715_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"343\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='343' height='387'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"343\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-aa0589780dd536aa458c24be689b4b08\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fa84c340ebd7f2d2643637c12021b715_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"343\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-aa0589780dd536aa458c24be689b4b08_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "谢 小潘 邀请.\n\n嗯.题主说的情况确实如此.我觉得原因可能如下.\n\n1.环境因素.比如空气污染,水源污染,食物污染等等.\n\n2.生活规律,和饮食习俗被打破,人类这个物种还没来得及适应.比如现在很多慢性病某种情况算是营养过剩,比如肥胖,2型糖尿病,高血脂等等.\n\n3.生活和工作压力变大,造成心理压力变大,记得有人说过,现在80%以上的人都有心理问题.所以我现在很怂的.只要没到底线,基本都是骂不还口的..........除了心理健康问题,还有不少疾病是心理应激影响免疫系统引起的.比如常见的,口疮,胃溃疡等等,...........\n\n4,不孕不育跟工业化有很大问题.比如常见的环境雌激素[1-7]",
